# Claude Code Execution Flow Diagram

## Complete Request-Response Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant REPL
    participant CLI
    participant Process
    participant Context
    participant Query
    participant API
    participant Engine
    participant Tools
    participant State
    participant UI
    
    User->>REPL: "Create component"
    REPL->>CLI: handleInput()
    
    Note over CLI: Parse slash commands<br/>Check attachments
    
    CLI->>Process: processUserInput()
    
    Process->>Process: Parse mentions
    Process->>Process: Attach files
    
    alt Hook blocking
        Process-->>UI: Show block reason
    end
    
    Process->>Context: buildContext()
    
    par Parallel context gathering
        Context->>Context: getGitStatus()
        Context->>Context: getBranch()
        Context->>Context: getMemoryFiles()
        Context->>Context: getProjectInfo()
    end
    
    Context-->>Query: Context + messages
    
    Query->>Engine: query()
    
    Engine->>API: messages.stream()
    
    loop Streaming events
        API-->>Engine: content_block_delta
        Engine->>Engine: Process event
        
        alt Text delta
            Engine->>UI: text event
        end
        
        alt Tool call start
            Engine->>UI: tool start
        end
        
        alt Tool input delta
            Engine->>UI: tool input
        end
        
        alt Tool complete
            Engine->>Tools: Execute tool
            
            Tools->>State: Check permission
            
            alt Not permitted
                State->>UI: Permission prompt
                UI-->>State: User approves
            end
            
            State-->>Tools: Proceed
            
            Tools->>Tools: Run tool
            
            loop Progress
                Tools->>UI: Progress update
            end
            
            Tools-->>Engine: Tool result
        end
    end
    
    API-->>Engine: message_stop
    Engine-->>Query: Complete
    Query-->>State: Update messages
    State-->>UI: Final state
    UI-->>User: Ready for next input
```

## Startup Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Entry as main.tsx
    participant Profile as Profiler
    participant MDM as MDM Read
    participant Keychain as Keychain
    participant Config as Config
    participant Auth as Auth
    participant MCP as MCP Servers
    participant State as AppState
    participant UI as Ink UI
    
    Entry->>Profile: profileCheckpoint('start')
    Entry->>MDM: startMdmRawRead()
    Entry->>Keychain: startKeychainPrefetch()
    
    Note over Entry,UI: ~135ms of module loading<br/>(MDM and Keychain run in parallel)
    
    Entry->>Profile: profileCheckpoint('loaded')
    
    par Configuration Loading
        Entry->>Config: Load settings
        Entry->>Auth: Check API key
    end
    
    Config-->>Entry: Settings loaded
    Auth-->>Entry: Auth ready
    
    Entry->>MCP: Connect servers
    
    MCP-->>Entry: Servers ready
    
    Entry->>State: Initialize store
    
    State-->>Entry: Store ready
    
    Entry->>UI: Render app
    UI-->>User: Welcome message
```

## Tool Execution Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START["Tool Call Detected"]
    
    START --> FIND["findToolByName()"]
    FIND --> TOOL{"Tool Found?"}
    
    TOOL -->|No| ERR1["Error: Tool not found"]
    TOOL -->|Yes| VALID["Validate Input"]
    
    VALID --> SCHEMA["JSON Schema validation"]
    SCHEMA --> VALID_OK{"Valid?"}
    
    VALID_OK -->|No| ERR2["Error: Invalid input"]
    VALID_OK -->|Yes| PERM["Check Permission"]
    
    PERM --> STATE["canUseTool()"]
    STATE --> PERM_OK{"Can Use?"}
    
    PERM_OK -->|No| REQUEST["Request Permission"]
    REQUEST --> USER{"User Response"}
    
    USER -->|Deny| ERR3["Permission Denied"]
    USER -->|Approve| PARTITION["Partition by Safety"]
    
    PERM_OK -->|Yes| PARTITION
    
    PARTITION --> SAFETY{"Concurrency Safe?"}
    
    SAFETY -->|Yes| PARALLEL["Run Concurrently"]
    SAFETY -->|No| SERIAL["Run Serially"]
    
    PARALLEL --> EXEC["Tool.execute()"]
    SERIAL --> EXEC
    
    EXEC --> PROGRESS{"Streaming?"}
    
    PROGRESS -->|Yes| STREAM["Yield progress events"]
    STREAM --> RESULT["Get result"]
    
    PROGRESS -->|No| RESULT
    
    RESULT --> FORMAT["Format result"]
    FORMAT --> SUCCESS["Success message"]
    
    ERR1 --> END
    ERR2 --> END
    ERR3 --> END
    SUCCESS --> END["Return to Query"]
```

## Permission State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Ready
    
    Ready --> Requesting: Tool called
    Requesting --> Approved: User approves
    Requesting --> Denied: User denies
    Approved --> Ready: Tool completes
    Denied --> Ready: Done
    
    Ready --> Bypass: permissionMode bypass
    Bypass --> Ready: Tool completes
    
    Note over Ready: canUseTool returns true
    Note over Requesting: UI shows prompt
    Note over Bypass: No prompt shown
```

## Context Compaction Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Query
    participant Engine
    participant Compact
    participant API
    participant Store
    
    Query->>Engine: Check tokens
    Engine-->>Query: At 85% limit
    
    Query->>Compact: Compact needed
    
    Compact->>Store: Get messages
    Store-->>Compact: messages[0..N]
    
    Compact->>Compact: findCompactBoundary()
    
    Note over Compact: Find oldest message<br/>that's safe to compact
    
    Compact->>Compact: Extract older messages
    Compact->>Compact: Keep recent messages
    
    Compact->>API: Summarize older
    API-->>Compact: Summary text
    
    Compact->>Compact: Create boundary message
    
    Note over Compact: boundary = {<br/>  type: compact_boundary,<br/>  summary: ...,<br/>  originalCount: 50<br/>}
    
    Compact->>Store: Replace with boundary
    
    Store-->>Compact: Updated
    
    Compact-->>Query: Compacted messages
    
    Query->>Engine: Continue with less context
```

## Session Management Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START["Session Start"]
    
    START --> GEN_ID["Generate Session ID"]
    GEN_ID --> INIT["Initialize State"]
    
    INIT --> LOAD["Load Session History?"]
    LOAD --> CHOICE{"User Choice"}
    
    CHOICE -->|New Session| EMPTY["Empty messages"]
    CHOICE -->|Resume| LOAD_SNAP["Load Snapshot"]
    CHOICE -->|Resume| PARSE_SNAP["Parse Session Data"]
    
    LOAD_SNAP --> PARSE_SNAP
    PARSE_SNAP --> RESTORE["Restore State"]
    
    EMPTY --> READY["Ready for Input"]
    RESTORE --> READY
    
    READY --> INPUT["User Input"]
    INPUT --> PROCESS["Process Input"]
    
    PROCESS --> NEW_MSG["Create Message"]
    NEW_MSG --> QUERY["Run Query"]
    
    QUERY --> EVENT{"Event Type"}
    
    EVENT -->|Text| DISPLAY["Stream to UI"]
    EVENT -->|Tool| EXEC["Execute Tool"]
    EVENT -->|Error| HANDLE["Handle Error"]
    
    DISPLAY --> MORE{"More Events?"}
    EXEC --> TOOL_RET["Tool Result"]
    HANDLE --> RECOVER["Recover?"]
    
    TOOL_RET --> ADD["Add to Messages"]
    ADD --> QUERY
    
    MORE -->|Yes| QUERY
    MORE -->|No| COMPLETE["Query Complete"]
    
    COMPLETE --> CHECK{"Should Compact?"}
    CHECK -->|Yes| COMPACT["Compact Context"]
    CHECK -->|No| READY
    
    RECOVER -->|Yes| QUERY
    RECOVER -->|No| FAIL["Log Error"]
    
    COMPACT --> READY
    
    READY --> EXIT["/exit Command"]
    EXIT --> SAVE["Save Session"]
    SAVE --> CLEANUP["Cleanup"]
    CLEANUP --> END["Process Exit"]
    
    FAIL --> SAVE
```

## Multi-Agent Coordination

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Main as Main Agent
    participant Task as Task Manager
    participant Agent1 as Sub-Agent A
    participant Agent2 as Sub-Agent B
    participant Tools as Tool System
    
    User->>Main: "Implement feature"
    
    Main->>Main: Analyze task
    
    Main->>Task: Create subtasks
    
    par Parallel execution
        Task->>Agent1: Task 1
        Task->>Agent2: Task 2
    end
    
    Agent1->>Tools: Use tools
    Agent2->>Tools: Use tools
    
    Tools-->>Agent1: Results
    Tools-->>Agent2: Results
    
    Agent1-->>Task: Task 1 done
    Agent2-->>Task: Task 2 done
    
    Task-->>Main: All tasks complete
    
    Main-->>User: Feature implemented
```

## Error Handling Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    ERROR["Error Occurs"]
    
    ERROR --> TYPE{"Error Type"}
    
    TYPE -->|API Error| RETRY{"Retryable?"}
    TYPE -->|Tool Error| REPORT["Report to AI"]
    TYPE -->|Permission| TRACK["Track Denial"]
    TYPE -->|Network| RETRY
    TYPE -->|Rate Limit| WAIT["Wait for Reset"]
    
    RETRY --> MAX{"At Max Retries?"}
    
    MAX -->|No| BACKOFF["Exponential Backoff"]
    BACKOFF --> RETRY_API["Retry Request"]
    RETRY_API --> SUCCESS{"Success?"}
    
    SUCCESS -->|Yes| CONTINUE["Continue"]
    SUCCESS -->|No| MAX
    
    MAX -->|Yes| FAIL["Fail Gracefully"]
    
    REPORT --> CONTINUE
    
    TRACK --> DENIALS{"3+ Denials?"}
    
    DENIALS -->|Yes| SUGGEST["Suggest Alternatives"]
    SUGGEST --> CONTINUE
    
    DENIALS -->|No| CONTINUE
    
    WAIT --> RESET{"Rate Reset?"}
    RESET -->|No| WAIT
    RESET -->|Yes| CONTINUE
    
    CONTINUE --> END["Resume"]
    FAIL --> END
```

## Hook System Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph HOOKS["Hook System"]
        H_BEFORE_Q["before_query"]
        H_AFTER_Q["after_query"]
        H_BEFORE_T["before_tool"]
        H_AFTER_T["after_tool"]
        H_ERROR["on_error"]
    end
    
    QUERY["Query Execution"]
    TOOL["Tool Execution"]
    
    QUERY --> H_BEFORE_Q
    
    H_BEFORE_Q --> BLOCK{"Blocked?"}
    BLOCK -->|Yes| HANDLE_B["Handle Block"]
    BLOCK -->|No| QUERY
    
    HANDLE_B --> ABORT["Abort Query"]
    
    QUERY --> H_AFTER_Q
    
    QUERY --> H_BEFORE_T
    H_BEFORE_T --> BLOCK_T{"Blocked?"}
    BLOCK_T -->|Yes| HANDLE_T["Handle Block"]
    BLOCK_T -->|No| TOOL
    
    TOOL --> H_AFTER_T
    
    QUERY --> H_ERROR
```

## Prefetch Optimization Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Entry as main.tsx
    participant MDM as MDM Raw
    participant Keychain as Keychain
    participant Imports as Module Imports
    participant Config as Config Loading
    
    Note over Entry,Imports: Time 0ms - Entry point called
    
    Entry->>Entry: profileCheckpoint(start)
    Entry->>MDM: startMdmRawRead()
    Entry->>Keychain: startKeychainPrefetch()
    
    Note over MDM,Keychain: Running in background
    Note over Imports: ~135ms of module loading
    
    Imports->>Config: Load all modules
    
    Config-->>Entry: Modules ready
    MDM-->>Entry: MDM data ready
    Keychain-->>Entry: Keychain data ready
    
    Entry->>Entry: All prefetch complete!
```
